Subject: [PATCH] net: dsa: mt7530: fix corrupt frames using trgmii on 40 MHz
 XTAL MT7621
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit
